import React ,{useState}from 'react'; import SubMenu from './SubMenu'; function menuShow(menu){ if(menu==="BRAND" || menu==="MENU" || menu==="EVENT" || menu==="ORDER"){ return "on" }else{ return "off" } } const Header = () => { const [menu, setMenu] = useState() console.log(menuShow(menu)) const handleMouseOver = (e) => { e.target.dataset.state = "open"; e.target.ariaExpanded= true; setMenu(e.target.innerHTML) if(menuShow(menu)=="on"){ setMenu('on') } }; const handleMouseOut = (e) => { e.target.dataset.state = "closed"; e.target.ariaExpanded= false; if(menuShow(menu)=="off"){ setMenu('No') } }; return ( <> < header class = "font-[DunkinSans] h-[clamp(60px,6.284vw,92px)] sticky top-0 text-espresso md:px-[10px] z-[60] bg-[url('/resources/images/common/header_bg.png')] bg-bottom lg:shadow-[0_0_20px_0_rgba(29,7,0,0.3)]" >

  • DUNKIN'

) } export default Header
